title: New Quan Yin Chay Vegetarian Food Garden
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Fast food, Take-out, Filipino
description: Moved here in 2014; formerly just Quan Yin Chay. Owned by Taoists, uses no garlic or onion. A la carte menu features many mock meat dishes that are already cooked and displayed in case. Sells take-away and frozen food.
